commit.message: Fix incorrect name of requirements file
Add sphinx autobuild to dev requirements

Change changelog version format

Prefix "v" to each version. This is done so that the documentation
generated via sphinx uses named anchors for version subheadings
(which will then remain consistent across revisions) instead of
autogenerating the anchors.
Move storage tests to their own files
Move each storage impl to its own file.
Add subsections for storage api docs
